vote.title: A public hearing to receive comments regarding an ordinance amending Chapter 51A, "Dallas Development Code", Ordinance No. 19455, as amended, of the Dallas City Code by amending Sections 51A-5.104 to meet the prerequisites of the Federal Emergency Management Agency Community Rating System Program which currently earns the property owners in Dallas a 25 percent discount on flood insurance premiums - Financing: No cost consideration to the City
